{"product_id":"madara-plum-plum-lip-balm-15ml","title":"MÁDARA Plum Plum Lip Balm 15ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eIntense hydration and heavenly softness from the very first application. Use alone for a sheer finish or as a base for your favorite lipstick. Lips stay soft, protected and hydrated to perfection. Formulated with deeply moisturising jojoba oil, shea butter and plum oil.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean, dry lips. Reapply whenever necessary. Use alone for a sheer finish or as a base for your favourite lipstick.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Cera Alba (Beeswax), Sorbitan olivate, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Prunus Domestica (Plum) Seed Oil, Aroma, Tocopherol, Calendula Officinalis (Calendula) Flower Extract, Chamomilla Recutita (Camomile) Flower Extract, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) Fruit Extract, Propolis Extract, Stevia Rebaudiana Extract, CI 77491 (Iron Oxides), Limonene, Linalool\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49887773229383,"sku":null,"price":10.4,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-plum-plum-lip-balm-15ml-844261.jpg?v=1739897244","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-plum-plum-lip-balm-15ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}